<!--<h4>FIRST BELT.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śubhamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> jayābhyudaya śālivāhana śakavarṣaṁbulu 145(7) Agunēṭi maṁ<unclear>nma</unclear>dha saṁvatsara kā<unclear>rttika</unclear>ba 12 Ānāṁṭi puṁṇyakālānanu śrīmadrājādhirāja rājapara 
</p>

<!--<h4>SECOND BELT.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="2" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> śrīvīra Acyutadēva mahārāyaluvāru <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ratnasiṁhāsanā rāḍulai pṛdhivī sā<unclear>ṁ</unclear>mrājyaṁ sēyu cuṁ<unclear>ḍaṁgā</unclear>nu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>THIRD BELT.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="3"/>śrīviṭhalēśvaradēva divyamāna divya śrīpādapadmaṁbulaku śrīmaṁmahānāyaṁka cāryyulayina kaṁ<unclear>bha</unclear>ṁ tiṁmānāyani veṁkaṭādrināyaniṁgāru <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <unclear>ṇā</unclear>mālōka <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> śrīAccu(cyu)tadēva mahārāyalu mākunāyaṁkurāsaku pāliṁca <gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <unclear>vi</unclear>ṭhalēśvaruni <unclear>pratimāśēśi</unclear> grāmaṁ kaṭṭiṁci Āgrāmānanu vanānanu 
</p>

<p>Fourth and fifth belts inscription are badly damaged.</p>

